Weightlifting vet takes aim at Trump in new ad with a surprise twist Weightlifting vet takes aim at Trump in new ad with a surprise twist Weightlifting vet takes aim at Trump in new ad with a surprise twist By Maggie Hendricks February 6, 2017 9:37 am 312 shares email By: Maggie Hendricks | February 6, 2017 9:37 am 
Vote Vets, a veterans group, released a commercial aimed at Donald Trump. Though it’s meant for the president, it’s probably going to motivate you, as well. Go ahead, watch it until the end. . @realDonaldTrump , we’re debuting this ad on @Morning_Joe , and taking it to other morning shows you watch, too! pic.twitter.com/LVINhUenaV 
If you’ll excuse me, I’m going to go to the gym for the next four hours. More Sports!
